@startuml
!theme blueprint
actor User
participant "Blazor Client" as Client
participant "Supabase API" as API
database "Supabase DB" as DB

== Оформление заказа ==

User -> Client : Нажать «Оформить заказ»
Client -> API : createOrder()
API -> DB : insert Order
DB --> API : OK
API --> Client : OrderId
Client --> User : Заказ оформлен

== Добавление отзыва ==

User -> Client : Отправить отзыв
Client -> API : addReview(productId, rating, text)
API -> DB : insert Review
DB --> API : OK
API --> Client : Success
Client --> User : Отзыв добавлен

@enduml
